Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在是裤头村的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:03.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is the early morning in bikini bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,此时水母们正在奔忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:06.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when the jellyfish are buzzing about
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,采着水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,making their jellyfish jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is happening here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Collectors?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course you are
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们特地给你做了一张网
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We made a net especially for you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想跟我们一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come with us?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你们一起捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing with you guys?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我看来  今天简直是最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be the best day ever in my book
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好想去捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would love to go jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't think of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休息日期间有什么更想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,anything I'd love to do more on my day off
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能比去捉水母更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than go jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尤其是跟我最好的两个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my two best friends
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:11.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我就是不行  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't, bye-bye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next time?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你们便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非太阳打西边出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that'll ever happen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也知道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:25.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像章鱼哥从来没有时间玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it always seems like Squidward never has time for fun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概是他不喜欢我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe he doesn't like us
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  你在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是他最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're his best friends
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll go
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还真把他们耍得团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure had them going
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨水母  快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid jellyfish, beat it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:59.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(737,788)}朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid's back
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:16.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid's home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要保证他被他两个最好的朋友欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we're going to make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's greeted by his two best friends
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那太棒了  他们谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, great, who are they?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Us
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:37.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(723,234)}欢迎回家
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让你今天变成最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to make this your best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你最美好的一天可不该在外边虚度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, your best day's sure not going to be out there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要喝汤来庆祝你最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some soup on your best day ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(709,626)}最美好的一天
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喝汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we go
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点烫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a little hot
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.05,0:06:13.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1103.005,392)}惨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:20.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1103.005,392)}很惨
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得不太适合拿汤来给他庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think soup is the best thing for him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on his best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不要听音乐来庆祝你最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about some music on your best day ever?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这音乐可是用你的竖笛来演奏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Played on your very own clarinet?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我嘴巴有点干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my lips are a little dry
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,音乐也不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:55.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Music isn't best, either
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们留了样压轴好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:59.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what is best is what we saved for last--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这大招肯定能成功让你最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one sure-fire thing to make your best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成为最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:05.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.57,0:07:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是水母田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:15.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is jellyfish fields
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,野生的水母们在这里遨游
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where wild jellyfish roam
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等待着我们来捉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just waiting to be captured
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, squid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,over here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道你急不可耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you're eager
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你连网都还没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you don't even have your net
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  帮他准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, fix him up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去给他找个范例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I find him a good specimen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用手把网抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Firmly grasp it in your hand
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把网抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Firmly grasp it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把网抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Firmly grasp it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ought to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前方有水母就位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one in position
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各就位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Set
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.16,0:07:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, squid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squidder
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  您能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you got it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉住它  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get it, Squidder
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们好像该给他示范怎么捉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we better show him how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  章鱼哥在捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Squid's doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.40,0:09:12.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼快捉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:12.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidster, you're doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这家伙不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This guy's good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.73,0:09:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是天生好手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a natural
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.61,0:09:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.36,0:09:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing great
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squid, go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续努力  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep doing it, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你都错过了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See what you've been missing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:00.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got it, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, Squid, go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用那张网
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Use that net
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟网合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be the net
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你感受到了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're feeling it, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带过来  把它一路带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the way, take him all the way
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥离成功就差最后六英里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The last six miles makes the Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got 'em now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's in the bag
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是不是你最美好的一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is really your best day ever, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:31.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.86,0:10:36.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得昨天进展很顺利  你说对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:36.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought yesterday went pretty well, don't you think?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玩得很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had fun
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here comes Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.12,0:10:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squid, how about that
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最美好得一天怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,best day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天永远都在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's always tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们为昨天的事情十分抱歉  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what happened yesterday, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要送你一份礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got you a present
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.73,0:11:09.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:09.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是昨天的那只
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, from yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没在生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not still mad, are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他还是很生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, he's still mad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.02,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(484,518)}痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\pos(419,310)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\pos(401,670)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\pos(505,262)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\pos(355,328)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz13.6\pos(441,626)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二号桌来一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:03.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty for table two
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:05.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(399,406)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我没一整天的时间跟你耗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I don't have the whole day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oui, oui
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一份蟹黄堡  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Une Krabby Patty, monsieur
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来个肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's les patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来  配料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next, l'ingredients
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来点芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Les mustard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能别装疯卖傻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you quit fooling around?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我蟹黄堡在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's my Krabby Patty?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Les hold on a second
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And voila
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在你鼻子底下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's under your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可笑死我了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're killing me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You really are
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at it, Squidward--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板送给裤头村老百姓的大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs' gift to all of bikini bottom--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  给我吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:02.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I swear, I'm not doing anything
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡闹鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.68,0:13:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Krabby Patty is haunted
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住  偷蟹黄堡的海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Avast, ye patty pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is no ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在偷我的财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stealin' me booty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听我说  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hear me, Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我搞明白你蟹黄堡的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I discover your formula for Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会让你破产的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll run you out of business
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我上过大学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went to college
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会放你的  小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll let you go, Squirt
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐飞碟去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on a flying saucer
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回海之霸去吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back to the chum bucket with you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你会付出代价的  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for this, Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(917,764)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是痞老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.42,0:13:47.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  他多年来都在偷我的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, he's been trying to steal
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me secret formula for years
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你就是偷不到对不对  小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But ye haven't got it yet, have ye, bug?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了小子  没那么好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough, lad, it wasn't that funny
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:11.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(311,282)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的蟹老板  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Krabs, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, me boy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(689,590)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Young man
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, over here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  靠近点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, boy, a little closer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Closer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:36.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that close
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这可恶的呆头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You blasted barnacle head
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.86,0:14:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to talk
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该算是朋友  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could say we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.28,0:14:51.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:51.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:53.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Acquaintances
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都是无脊椎动物是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we're both invertebrates, aren't we?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  这不挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, everything works out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有样东西要送你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have something for you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直把它放在我的秘密细胞区室里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been keeping it in my secret compartment
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.22,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 细胞区室：具有界膜的细胞器总称\N如叶绿体、线粒体等 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪闪发亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sparkle, sparkle
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一把黄金锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:15.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A golden spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面还刻着我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:17.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's even got my name on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a gift
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A gift from a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友间就要互相赠送礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friends give each other gifts
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且明天是我生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And tomorrow is my birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.36,0:15:32.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我在这世上最想要的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what I'd like more than anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:32.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the whole wide world?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿童垫高椅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A booster seat?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,儿童垫高椅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Booster seat?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想要你  也就是我朋友在生日那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I want for my birthday from you, my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is one of those
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鲜嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tender
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美味的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,delicious
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想当我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just want to be friends
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样你就能把蟹黄堡弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you can get your hands on a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且明天也肯定不是你生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I bet it's not even your birthday tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为你很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:15:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I thought you were stupid
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对不会从我手上弄到蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get a Krabby Patty from me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当了朋友也弄不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if we are friends
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,弄不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会弄到蟹黄堡的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.65,0:16:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你会一个人亲手把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you're going to hand-deliver it to me personally
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这低能的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You weak-minded fool
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.02,0:16:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你会是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.85,0:16:49.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,字母表中字母妙  ABC
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:49.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Letters of the alphabet, a, b, c
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该就在这附近才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It should be in here somewhere
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就要开始玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will be the beginning of the end
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid brain
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点回来  你这头猪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back here, you swine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了  大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, brain
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going down
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's grand
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.04,0:17:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在开始我受过大学教育的详尽计划
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, for my very elaborate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and college-educated plan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(513,874)}控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1079,702)}大脑
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是时候要让你醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now it's time for a little wakey-uppy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(989,936)}总控
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经早上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning already?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我今天感觉有点怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel a little funny today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我控制住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have you now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该吃营养均衡的早餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for a well-balanced breakfast
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心里想的可不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't what I had in mind
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我拿下裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me just grab my pants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来今天我不穿裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not wearing any pants today
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我也用不上门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm not using the door, either
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you later, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there is something wrong with me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.76,0:18:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need some help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.65,0:18:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在跟你说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:59.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to you
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.49,0:19:09.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你这滥竽充数的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:09.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, you mediocre clarinet player
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滥竽充数
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mediocre?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.38,0:19:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这自负过头的十八线小艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You pretentious little insignificant artist
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.34,0:19:18.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的可悲创作所蕴含的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:18.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your sniveling creations are worth less
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比原生动物的排泄物还要低
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than a protozoan's waste
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑子肯定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something must be wrong with my brain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你算什么样的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of friend are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nonsense
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正你也没喜欢过我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You never liked me, anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你甚至都不来参加我生日派对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't even come to my birthday party
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of my head
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别来碰我的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Leave my brain alone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:07.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(569,410)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打包外带怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about a little takeout?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,never
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗不了我  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:08.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't fool me, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是想要蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(445,696)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且你会一个人亲手把它交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are going to hand-deliver it to me personally
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面没人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no one here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着你说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't remind me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:24.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(967,244)}厨房
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我准备好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Brace yourself, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my lab
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(851.184,922)}拉布拉多犬
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这是我的实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is my laboratory
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我先前给你听过我的留声机了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:33.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And did I ever show you my record player?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must fight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.10,0:20:54.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:54.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有你帮忙事情就好办多了吧  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you see how much easier it is when you help, friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,觉得我的分析仪怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:01.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you like my analyzer?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便放个什么东西都能分析出成分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tells the ingredients of whatever I put into it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:08.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(763,460)}海藻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(1129,414)}50%{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(1085,656)}50%{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}藻
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,佩服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.29,0:21:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impressed?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来揭露秘密配方的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's reveal that secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根小小的手指头把蟹黄堡带了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this little piggy brought home a Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根小小的手指头会帮我把它放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This little piggy will help me drop it in
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有最后的遗言吗  泄密宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any last words, SpongeBob SecretPants?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.14,0:21:37.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很对不起  我让蟹老板失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:37.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just have to say I'm sorry I let Mr. Krabs down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让全裤头村的百姓失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let all of bikini bottom down
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最糟的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But worst of all
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我让你失望了  娇嫩的小蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I let you down you delicate little Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有着美味多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With your tasty, juicy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可口温暖又冒气的精华
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,scrumptious warm, steamy goodness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冒气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steamy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.37,0:21:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我永远不会忘记你的高度秘密肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget your 100% all-secret patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,秘密地配着海底奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,secretly assembled with undersea cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:01.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pickle
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lettuce
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.05,0:22:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tomato
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洋葱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:03.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,onion
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.59,0:22:08.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都在松软的海草籽面包之间蒸熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all secretly steaming between
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two fluffy seaweed-seed buns
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.76,0:22:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快到爸爸这来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come to papa
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.14,0:22:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620.864,406)}痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(1074.925,404)}1%{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(942.741,712)}99%{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}热废气
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡  我们现在可以回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patty, I guess we can go home now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.83,0:22:36.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那是我的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:36.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, that's my Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还回来  你这浑身是孔的怪胎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back, you porous freak
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I command you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My patty
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是将就卖点薯条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll settle for some fries
